Class RatioCullOperator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.deeplearning4j.arbiter.optimize.generator.genetic.culling.RatioCullOperator

    public abstract class RatioCullOperator
extends Object
implements CullOperator
    An abstract base for cull operators that culls back the population to a ratio of its maximum size.

    Alexandre Boulanger

    • Constructor Detail

      • RatioCullOperator

        public RatioCullOperator(double cullRatio)
        Parameters:
        cullRatio - The ratio of the maximum population size to be culled.
        For example, a ratio of 1/3 on a population with a maximum size of 30 will cull back a given population to 20.

      • RatioCullOperator
